{"tid":1020331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向菲警潑豆腐花　支那污染物留學生流淚致歉　副總統：支那人不斷增加 享特殊待遇","createTime":"2019-02-13T13:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T14:00:42.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3051ada690958df262024a349b1291d574cf46d1","tid":1020331,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T13:51:28.000Z","msg":"竟然由菲律賓黑警幫全世界出一啖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%90%91%E8%8F%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%BD%91%E8%B1%86%E8%85%90%E8%8A%B1-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B5%81%E6%B7%9A%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89-%E5%89%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0-%E4%BA%AB%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E5%BE%85%E9%81%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%258F%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BD%2591%25E8%25B1%2586%25E8%2585%2590%25E8%258A%25B1-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%25B7%259A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%2589-%25E5%2589%25AF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%25AE%258A%25E5%25BE%2585%25E9%2581%2587%2F&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=5e234aea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%258F%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BD%2591%25E8%25B1%2586%25E8%2585%2590%25E8%258A%25B1-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%25B7%259A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%2589-%25E5%2589%25AF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%25AE%258A%25E5%25BE%2585%25E9%2581%2587%2F&h=01475740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%90%91%E8%8F%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%BD%91%E8%B1%86%E8%85%90%E8%8A%B1-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B5%81%E6%B7%9A%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89-%E5%89%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0-%E4%BA%AB%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E5%BE%85%E9%81%87/</a><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓一名中國女留學生上周六（9日）因被阻止攜帶豆腐花進入馬尼拉地鐵，一怒之下將豆腐花潑向一名警員，被控襲擊等罪名，事件在當地引發軒然大波。張佳樂昨日獲保釋候審，馬尼拉警察局長Guillermo Eleazar 專程到場在傳媒面前親自訓斥該名女留學生，指就算是被拘捕的罪犯，或是毒犯都不會如此不尊重警員。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起菲律賓政界關注，菲律賓副總統羅布雷多（Leni Robredo）批評，事件不僅是對執法人員的侮辱，也是對菲律賓人的侮辱，更是反映中國人享受「特殊待遇」（special treatment）的「警號」。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的菲律賓留學的23歲中國籍女子張佳樂（音譯，Jiale Zhang），周二保釋後接受傳媒訪問，她在鏡頭前含淚道歉。她解釋，事件發生當日她的情緒低落，因此一時失控，她感到很後悔。她在菲律賓居住了六年，希望能給予她改過的機會。張佳樂說：「我真的很喜歡菲律賓，所以我住在這裏。我喜歡這裏的人。（I really like the Philippines that's why I stay here. I like people here. I really love Filipinos.）」<br />\n<br />\n馬尼拉地區警察局長 Guillermo Eleazar 到場當面批評她的行為。他稱，即使是毒犯或罪犯，也不會如此對待警員，「明顯不尊重警員，我們不會就此算數。我們接納她的道歉，但她亦要為自己行為承擔責任。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張除了面臨襲擊等控罪之外，當地警方有意入境部門申請，以不受歡迎人物為由，驅逐她出境。事件引發菲律賓政界討論。菲律賓外長洛欽（Teddy Locsin）認同應檢控她，但質疑是否有需要將她驅逐出境，「她是一名學生，來這裡升學，也顯示了她對我們的信心。」<br />\n<br />\n副總統羅布雷多稱，來到菲律賓的中國公民不斷增加，今次事件是反映中國人享受「特殊待遇」（special treatment）的「警號」（wake-up call）。她又再次提及愈來愈多中國人在菲律賓工作，影響了本地人的生計。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y517H5icR0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY517H5icR0k&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1a80eda1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y517H5icR0k</a>"},{"pid":"554060c657d0617b46c9928dc20c6bef29ecc248","tid":1020331,"uid":65186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"菲律賓都唔係乜好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}